\f2\b\fs48 \cf2 \cb3 2) Add a modern 
\f4\fs38\fsmilli19200 \cb5 theme.json
\f2\fs48 \cb3  (v3)\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 Here\'92s a compact starter you can expand later:\cb1 \
